title: Corpus fund: An amount of Rs
clause_text: Corpus fund: An amount of Rs.40000 or as may be decided by SRA as per Regulation No 33(10) shall be deposited with MCGM for each eligible slum dwellers
section: 33(6) Reconstruction of buildings destroyed by fire or which have collapsed or which have been demolished under lawful order
